ATTRIBUTION REQUIREMENTS:
Any website or application using this code MUST include visible attribution
to the original author. This attribution must be:
- Permanently visible on the website (not hidden behind clicks, hovers, or toggles)
- Include a link to the original repository: https://github.com/Davicjc/Portfolio-CJC
- Include the original author's name: "Davi Castro"
- Be placed in a reasonable location such as the footer or about section

PERSONAL CONTENT RESTRICTIONS:
Users are PROHIBITED from using any personal documents, content, or information
from this portfolio, including but not limited to:
- Resume/CV files (curriculo.pdf)
- Personal certificates and certifications
- Profile pictures or personal photos
- Personal contact information
- Specific work experiences, education history, or personal projects described in the content
- Any content from the documentos/ folder

Example of proper attribution:
"Design based on portfolio by Davi Castro (https://github.com/Davicjc/Portfolio-CJC)"

